reviewText:
Absolutely love this series!  The packaging was great as well as DVD are great.  No skipping or snowy images like some I've purchased :-)
Overall, I would give this purchase 5 stars !

Ok... I LOVE the Bionic Woman... have purchased the first two seasons myself..... But DON'T buy this "Combo Pack".... They are charging 25 bucks more for this than if you were to purchase all three seasons separately.... RIDICULOUS!

It gets better with age and we are loving this series all over again and our children for the first time.

Thank you.
Just want I was hoping for
I love this show.  I'm having a blast watching the series right from the beginning.
Love the Dvd'S. The sound goes in and out on a lot of the episodes. Not sure if this is a defect on the ones I got or just a general defect because they are old shows.
Awesome. A must have for those Bionic Woman fans.
just what I expected... nice set
